{"tid":1848484,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"今日起華航集團台港澳線停供熱餐毛毯枕頭","createTime":"2020-01-28T13:12:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-28T14:19:21.000Z","uid":17646,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"616c8319e0d5b35e03461590d229623f35b3c6ef","tid":1848484,"uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T13:12:20.000Z","msg":"因應新型冠狀病毒疫情，華航集團（包括中華航空、華信航空、台灣虎航）宣布將提高防疫措施，今天開始調整兩岸及台港澳航線機上餐飲及用品服務內容；<br />\n全艙等均採「無熱餐」服務，不提供毛毯、枕頭、毛巾、報章雜誌等。<br />\n主要考量減少人員接觸、減少非必要重複用品使用並調整為一次性用品，<br />\n同時亦鼓勵自備環保杯等自用品，以降低傳染風險。<br />\n<br />\n買左商務個班真係多撚謝武漢"},{"pid":"09852a5e48e413acdc6d475089d8b8bb17ae59ff","tid":1848484,"uid":205482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T13:13:06.000Z","msg":"死性不改 1.29罷佢老母<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1848465\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1848465</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"330d2b34445b6733c8ee75440507a54c41913e63","tid":1848484,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T13:13:29.000Z","msg":"屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c03c2bdce3eb542bfb2bef2e29ee43f436334f92","tid":1848484,"uid":192732,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T13:15:06.000Z","msg":"依啲應該唔算慘，好似有人book左機票酒店但冇得去<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58b4515bc0fcb8e790ff8ce3e85c068644d269bd","tid":1848484,"uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c03c2bdce3eb542bfb2bef2e29ee43f436334f92","tid":1848484,"uid":192732,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T13:15:06.000Z","msg":"依啲應該唔算慘，好似有人book左機票酒店但冇得去<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T13:19:22.000Z","msg":"點解無得去呢"},{"pid":"00effdb34dffdebe3b6fc252ca4ee9607ea78632","tid":1848484,"uid":345458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T13:19:46.000Z","msg":"入去推10下！<br />\n<br />\